Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,八云…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的…跟八云交换身分了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,《绯红结系》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,倦怠感 losing yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,尚未找到建立关系的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有个麻烦的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,至死都在寻求某人的拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在得以喘息的混沌虚无之间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,以输赢之间为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,注意别让信任走向尽头 务必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see I'm always on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,今天仍拼命地联系着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你脑中那冷感的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,摇滚的日子未曾有过的浩劫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,光荣早已埋葬在某处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这一瞬间寂寞孤独的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,与机关枪射出的子弹并列
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,射穿所有世间道理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,今天仍拼命地联系着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,与机关枪射出的子弹并列
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也仍在一起 清晰地联系着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你那脑中冷感的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(沉睡的思念)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,跟以往…不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这两千年来 他都在这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连 有件事希望你协助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为了消灭岐之门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请你祝我们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你在荒吐神时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,使用了红色系线跳跃时空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而接触到两千年前的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因此出现了维度纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只要维度纠缠存在\N岐之门就不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去 世界会毁灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你得解开纠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,解决不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让维度纠缠出现的人\N才能解开其纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都成功了 所以没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那为何不帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我解决不了 这就是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连 当初你为了救艾丽斯\N才跳跃了时空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但 为何跳跃到两千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,刚开始…我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,八云皇 可能是红色系线的脑力者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 或许我是受到他的牵引吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,无预警地跳跃到两千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我拼命地寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能拯救两千年后艾丽斯的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,能改变未来的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到的答案 就是成为八云皇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,利用建国之父的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,应该能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,做些什么 那你做到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在遥远的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能拯救艾丽斯的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我自己与荒吐神连结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,与所有系统的中枢荒吐神连结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就能驱动历史
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就能拯救艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以荒吐神也是\N脑部组成的生物计算机啰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,强制入侵我们脑部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也是你搞的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 艾丽斯她…她无法复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我才不断重复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不断重复…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,跳跃时空数次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,成为八云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,维度纠缠也因此产生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我解开维度纠缠 也解决不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我会产生新的纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连 有两人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为何 你在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你会在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我才想问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只要成为八云 与荒吐神连结
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就有可能是拯救艾丽斯的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,跳跃时空 留在荒吐神里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所有尝试错误纪录证明过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那我为何无法跳跃到两千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为何我跳跃时空失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮过你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快交出所有的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还有记忆… 我要吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的与荒吐神连结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的记忆 都是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么\N-难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你得到了荒吐神的情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不论你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都不超过几百…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,几千…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,几万分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我以外的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我把相同情报给无数的我多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此 仍无法改变未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,无法救艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,观察到这一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你只会白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无所获
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,无限循环中的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别再妄想了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要救艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不管几次 我都要救艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个 把红色系线交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以跳跃时间失败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是没成功复制结人的超脑力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是哥哥的超脑力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也很难持续持有红色系线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才要一直复制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你们抵抗也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到红色系线是必然的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,跳跃时空 会毁灭世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不论要用什么手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我都要再跳跃一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不打算协助我们啰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,新日向和月球 虽然有许多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但世界毁灭的话就什么都无法解决
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须创造出新的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,以这样的历史织罗而成的世界\N一点价值也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这次一定要改变成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解你想救艾丽斯的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要妳的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妳也不可能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,超脑力增强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,结人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能放弃重要的事物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,通过许多艰难的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救这颗星球的红色守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,两位年轻的绯红守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那岐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,结人皇上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对上 那岐卡门上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 今天天气好像不错喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,成为怪伐军 是你从小的愿望嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要出去走走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我有想逛的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那岐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,结人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾想过 回到过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,救我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是结人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妳很后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果 当时那瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,妳注意到异状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不会变成这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你很后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果 当时那瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那岐人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他被带到医院后 就没跟我联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你来找我 就不会演变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我…变得莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要我杀你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在耳边响起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明不想战斗 这么厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害怕 却无法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确 后悔过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只要做出稍微不同的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,未来 或许就会不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,无论何时 我们只能做出一种选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,人活着 就得做出选择往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只能做出 当下最正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,结果你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为了自已的私欲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而把重要事物一脚踢开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的思念不过就这点程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 正因为有那岐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,别说得一副你很懂似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为有那岐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是那岐 任何人发生什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都不能闭上眼睛否认一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的体悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而是前往未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们非这么做不可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你们的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃过去 否认已发生的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是逃避问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何我都要救艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该有 艾丽斯期望你\N走向未来的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丽斯并不希望\N毁灭世界来拯救自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不准提艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你应该能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你与荒吐神连结了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快想起艾丽斯的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就算知道什么\N我也不会改变想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不管有多么困难…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不会改变…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,红色系线交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,重 我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只要得到红色系线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,重 跟卡连一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,从荒吐神的记忆里寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找艾丽斯真正的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她是位很好的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能让你如此思念她\N便是最好的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,总是帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是今天 因此害他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那绝非一点皮肉伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是希望他别再帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而是希望 他能更加善待自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我想一直跟他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此 他还是会继续保护妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我得更努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让卡连不再为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而持续加油努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我希望 卡连能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连崔佛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你过得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丽斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我 不认同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不认同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,结人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经复制你的红色系线了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丽斯真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,艾丽斯妳等着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这次一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能救艾丽斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,结人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,卡连
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,被追求的憧憬所困
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,揭开被阻挡的摇曳阳炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a stranger in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,从未见过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,自己能不再恐惧翱翔高空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm spreading my wings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,华丽舞步的鸟儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,仰望染红的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,追过了强风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,景色蔓延在千变万化的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在交错的光芒中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,持续寻找明天的行径方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's in your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me now you're afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to waste
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不再畏惧何物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Into a brand new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,(消灭岐之门作战)
